 <h4>Finite element formulation</h4>
 <!-- <span class="eq"><var>u</var> = 0</span> , <span class="eq"><var>v</var> = 0</span> , <span class="eq"><var><span class="vec">⃗</span>z</var> = <span class="b0">[</span>0; 0<span class="b0">]</span> = <b class="b0">[</b>0 0<b class="b0">]</b></span> -->
 <p>We will formulate a 2D truss element with 3rd order geometric nonlinearity. The equilibrium equations will be derived in local CS, for the deformed state of the structure, assuming large displacements, as follows:</p>
 <img alt="nonlin-truss-element.png" src="./Images/nonlin-truss-element.png" style="height:115pt; width:198pt;"/>
