   <span class="b0">]</span>
  </span>
 </p>
 <p>Partial element Jacobi matrix</p>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <var>J</var>
   <sub>e</sub>
   (
   <var>e</var>
   )  =
   <var>t</var>
   (
