   <sup>-5</sup>
  </span>
 </p>
 <p>Iteratively calculate the following equations of the Newton-Raphson’s method:</p>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <var>
    <span class="vec">⃗</span>
    Z
   </var>
   <sub>0</sub>
   =
